            <Property Name="Font" Value="Arial-16" />
            <Property Name="Text" >This is a classic Mahjong Solitaire game. It is a first brick in the long road to an Open source RPG we (OGS team) wish to create.
 
[image='set:Logos image:OGS'] team:
Michael Kapelko - code and content;
Ivan Korystin - gameplay design, content and QA.
 
Third-party resources:
Raquel Ravanini - images for "Classic"  theme.
Kevin MacLeod - all tracks in "Eastern" and "Piano" music packs. Tracks "Funkorama", "Neo Western" and "Protofunk" in "Modern" music pack.
Dano - Tracks "Crazy from the message", "King or an alien", "Sun spark", "The time isnt right", "The wire" and "Today then tomorrow" in "Modern" music pack.
Fenster - Track "Free Software" in "Modern" music pack.
 
More info on third-party resources, their licenses and copyrights you can find in README files, placed in themes or music packs directories.
 
Libraries:
[image='set:Logos image:OGRE'] with [image='set:Logos image:OpenGL'] backend
 
[image='set:Logos image:CEGUI']
 
[image='set:Logos image:OpenAL']
 
Thanks to:
- Ogre3D team/community for the engine and help;
- Lightfeather team/community for help while this game has been using Lightfeather engine;
- OpenAL-Soft/ALURE developer KittyCat for help.
Special thanks to CrazyEddie for good GUI system and great support.
 
